OOC: Didn&#39;t Grounded stop the explosions with those vine things?

Burning Hammer held onto Lambda tight. The explosion blew Zeni backwards and
into the wall.

Arrow: What the hell was that!?

Arrow stepped backwards as the flames hit him. He was a little singed, as
the explosion was pretty blocked by the vines and walls between the room
they were in and the one with the bombs.

Burning Hammer: I guess we have some repair work to do, now.

Arrow: How fun.

Arrow pulled Zeni up by an arm.

Arrow: Don&#39;t get knocked over so easily, the opponent would take advantage
of it.

Perplex came out of a CR Chamber.

Perplex: Hey guys, battle over?

Arrow: No.

Perplex: Then what are we waiting for?

Burning Hammer: Perplex. Sorry for putting a tracking device in you.

Perplex: What? How&#39;d you remember that?

Burning Hammer: Just did.

Perplex watches Burning Hammer cautiously, then turns to the door.

Perplex: I want command over the shields so I can open them when I want to.

Arrow: Same thing I want, Perplex, but come here, first.

Arrow led Perplex to the weapons room. Everything was knocked over and
destroyed from the explosion, but the weapons seemed fine. Stranato did a
crappy job. Arrow pulled several weapons from the rubble and gave them to
Perplex.

Arrow: You have to use these.

Perplex: Arrow, I--

Arrow: Shhh! Zenith told me you were wary about weapons, but you need to
forget that now. We&#39;re vigilantes, we have to fight to defeat evil like
those Maximals and Deemos. Now do what you must. You think you&#39;re strong
without weapons, but you&#39;re not. We have to fight with everything we have.

Perplex: Okay.

He takes the weapons and follows Arrow back to the door.

Arrow: Open the shields again, we need to return to the battle.

Zeni: Can I come?

Arrow: Are you going to fight?

Zeni: Yeah, I&#39;m really going to win.

Perplex: Arrow, no.

Arrow: Come with us then.

Zeni: Yeah!

Perplex: No!

Arrow: I said yes! Don&#39;t be trying to change my command, he&#39;s not your kid!

Perplex: He&#39;s more mine than your&#39;s!

Arrow: Only in your dreams.

Arrow whispering: Besides, we need a decoy. We won&#39;t let him get hurt too
bad.

Perplex: I can&#39;t let you do that, Arrow.

Arrow: You can&#39;t do a thing to stop me.

Perplex: His death rests on on your shoulders, Arrow. I&#39;ll gut you like a
fish.

Arrow: Relax, partner. I&#39;m the expert, remember?

Perplex: Well--

Arrow: Shhh! Okay little guy, let&#39;s see what you&#39;ve got.

Perplex: Arrow--

Arrow: Shhh! Alright, open the shield or else give me control over it...

